OL,6,FMembers of the public are invited to
OL,7,Fgather at Exchange Flags for the
OL,8,Fsilence, led by the Lord Mayor of
OL,9,FLiverpool Mary Rasmussen.
OL,11,FA spokeswoman for Liverpool City
OL,12,FCouncil said flags will be flown at
OL,13,Fhalf-mast on civic buildings and the
OL,14,Ftown hall will light up red in the
OL,15,Fevening in tribute.
OL,17,FA specially designed bench to
OL,18,Frecognise survivors of the disaster
OL,19,Fwas unveiled at Anfield on Friday, 12
OL,20,FApril.
