OL,6,FIn 2021, retired officers Donald
OL,7,FDenton and Alan Foster and former
OL,8,Fforce solicitor Peter Metcalf, who
OL,9,Fwere accused of amending statements to
OL,10,Fminimise the blame on South Yorkshire
OL,11,FPolice, were acquitted of perverting
OL,12,Fthe course of justice after a judge
OL,13,Fruled there was no case to answer.
OL,15,FFamilies have campaigned for a to help
OL,16,Fvictims of major disasters get justice.
OL,18,FA spokesman for the campaign said:
OL,19,F"The pain and suffering of the past 35
OL,20,Fyears have not diminished.
