OL,3,CLiverpool to fall silent to mark 35
OL,4,Cyears since Hillsborough disaster
OL,6,F"Today, we pay tribute to all 97
OL,7,Fsupporters, they will never be
OL,8,Fforgotten, and we fight on in their
OL,9,Fmemory and for all those who have
OL,10,Fsuffered such injustice at the hands
OL,11,Fof the state.
OL,13,F"The truth of what really happened on
OL,14,Fthat dreadful day was not revealed for
OL,15,Fdecades because public authorities and
OL,16,Fofficials concealed the truth in their
OL,17,Fown interests.
