OL,3,CLiverpool to fall silent to mark 35
OL,4,Cyears since Hillsborough disaster
OL,6,F"Yet 35 years on, the experiences of
OL,7,FHillsborough families have been
OL,8,Frepeated countless times, currently
OL,9,Fwith the Post Office scandal. Little
OL,10,Fhas changed.
OL,12,F"A Hillsborough Law, with a duty of
OL,13,Fcandour at its heart, would ensure
OL,14,Fthat the battles faced by the
OL,15,FHillsborough and Post Office families,
OL,16,Fand countless others, can never be
OL,17,Frepeated.
