OL,3,CLiverpool to fall silent to mark 35
OL,4,Cyears since Hillsborough disaster
OL,6,F"It would create a legal duty on
OL,7,Fpublic authorities and officials to
OL,8,Ftell the truth and proactively co-
OL,9,Foperate with official investigations
OL,10,Fand inquiries.
OL,12,F"Sir Keir Starmer has pledged to make
OL,13,Fthis law a reality if the Labour Party
OL,14,Fcomes to power, we hope other parties
OL,15,Fwill follow suit and stop this
OL,16,Fcriminal abuse of power."
